{"id": "16330", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16330", "title": "Measure", "text": "Measure is a &lt;a href=\"suffix\"&gt;suffix&lt;/a&gt; that can appear on &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;. It provides a small bonus to Minimum &lt;a href=\"Damage\"&gt;Damage&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt can start spawning on items at &lt;a href=\"Item%20Level\"&gt;Item Level&lt;/a&gt; 12, but will not be able to spawn on all items until level 37. Some items also are not able to acquire full effect. \nStats.\n\"Can appear on:\" &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic Items&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;\n\"Is available on:\" &lt;a href=\"Amulets\"&gt;Amulets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Circlets\"&gt;Circlets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rings\"&gt;Rings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Weapons\"&gt;Weapons&lt;/a&gt; (except &lt;a href=\"Wands\"&gt;Wands&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Staves\"&gt;Staves&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Orbs\"&gt;Orbs&lt;/a&gt;)"}
{"id": "54643", "revid": "46404728", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=54643", "title": "Meat or Treat", "text": "Meat or Treat was a Halloween-themed event for \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\". It launched on October 29, 2024 and lasted until November 5, 2024. It had event-exclusive cosmetics and encounters.\nGameplay.\nDuring the event, players could \"meat or treat\" using &lt;a href=\"Shrines%20%28Diablo%20IV%29\"&gt;shrines&lt;/a&gt; within &lt;a href=\"Dungeon%20%28Diablo%20IV%29\"&gt;dungeons&lt;/a&gt;. Activating the shrine could spawn &lt;a href=\"Treasure%20Goblin\"&gt;Treasure Goblin&lt;/a&gt;s or &lt;a href=\"Burning%20Butcher\"&gt;Burning Butcher&lt;/a&gt; demons. A \"cobweb-covered Cosmetic straight from Sarat\u2019s Lair\" set, &lt;a href=\"Hallowed%20Treasures\"&gt;Hallowed Treasures&lt;/a&gt;, could be claimed from the shop while the event was active."}
