{"id": "41455", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41455", "title": "Mercenary Batum", "text": "Batum was a mercenary employed by the &lt;a href=\"Ashwold%20Guard\"&gt;Ashwold Guard&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, the Guard employed him to track down the leader of &lt;a href=\"Grave%20Robber\"&gt;grave robbers&lt;/a&gt; that were plundering &lt;a href=\"Ashwold%20Cemetery\"&gt;Ashwold Cemetery&lt;/a&gt;\u2014&lt;a href=\"Gorman\"&gt;Gorman&lt;/a&gt;. He located him at a camp, but Gorman refused to come out unless it was safe. However, the grave robbers created a signal by burning the poison glands of scorpions; a fact that he realized could be used to draw Gorman out of hiding, and in doing so, kill him. He asked a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;hero/group of heroes&lt;/a&gt; to recover the glands, so that a false signal could be created. The hero(s) succeeded, and Gorman gave them a share of the profit, saying that they'd make a fine mercenary/mercenaries.\nIn-game.\nBatum is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". He is found in &lt;a href=\"The%20Outskirts\"&gt;The Outskirts&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Ashwold%20Cemetery\"&gt;Ashwold Cemetery&lt;/a&gt;. Talking to him will start the \"&lt;a href=\"Sending%20the%20Signal\"&gt;Sending the Signal&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"dynamic%20event\"&gt;dynamic event&lt;/a&gt;."}
