{"id": "16975", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16975", "title": "Meteor (monster skill)", "text": "Meteor is a &lt;a href=\"monster\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt; skill not unlike the similar skill used by the various &lt;a href=\"Sorceress\"&gt;Sorceress&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Wizard\"&gt;Wizard&lt;/a&gt; classes.\nIn \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\", it is used by some variants of &lt;a href=\"Vampire\"&gt;Vampire&lt;/a&gt;s. \nIn \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\" it is used by &lt;a href=\"Ifriss%20the%20Destroyer\"&gt;Ifriss the Destroyer&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Beledwe\"&gt;Beledwe&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Sanctifier%20Proxy\"&gt;Sanctifier Proxy&lt;/a&gt;s. Additionally, &lt;a href=\"arcane\"&gt;arcane&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=\"Aeshama\"&gt;Aeshama&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Othva\"&gt;Othva&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gorgos\"&gt;Gorgos&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gorgothra\"&gt;Gorgothra&lt;/a&gt;), &lt;a href=\"ice\"&gt;ice&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=\"Vitaath\"&gt;Vitaath&lt;/a&gt;) and &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=\"Gebdu\"&gt;Gebdu&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ophinneb\"&gt;Ophinneb&lt;/a&gt;) variants of this skill are featured in Diablo Immortal."}
