{"id": "29063", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=29063", "title": "Meticulous Bolts", "text": "Meticulous Bolts were a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"quivers\"&gt;quiver&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=\"Demon%20Hunter\"&gt;Demon Hunter&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It required &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 50 to drop. In patch 2.1, it replaced the &lt;a href=\"Flint%20Ripper%20Arrowheads\"&gt;Flint Ripper Arrowheads&lt;/a&gt;, and in patch 2.4.1, it was removed and replaced with the more versatile &lt;a href=\"Augustine%27s%20Panacea\"&gt;Augustine's Panacea&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe unique affix only affected one rune of the &lt;a href=\"Elemental%20Arrow\"&gt;Elemental Arrow&lt;/a&gt;, essentially allowing it to zap each target more times before it travels too far from it. Total distance it covers did not change.\nDespite the Game Guide stating that it had 3 random affixes, it actually had 4, to a total of 7 (like any other Legendary Quiver)."}
{"id": "50073", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50073", "title": "Mhar", "text": "Mhar is a member of the &lt;a href=\"Taan\"&gt;Taan&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Mage%20Clan\"&gt;Mage Clan&lt;/a&gt;. He is a Juris at the &lt;a href=\"Taan%20Star%20Observatory\"&gt;Taan Star Observatory&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nMhar was part of (or at least present) the Juris body that sentenced &lt;a href=\"Karshun\"&gt;Karshun&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Othva\"&gt;Othva&lt;/a&gt; for the Astral Bloom \"incident\". In his report, he expressed his opinion that the judgement was insufficient. However, he didn't disapprove of it, as he believed that \"their presence invited madness\".\nBy &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231272\"&gt;1272&lt;/a&gt;, Taan Star Observatory was attacked by the &lt;a href=\"Cult%20of%20Terror\"&gt;Cult of Terror&lt;/a&gt;. Mhar, along with &lt;a href=\"Sunithi\"&gt;Sunithi&lt;/a&gt;, were among the defenders.\nIn-game.\nMhar appears as an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". He is featured in the &lt;a href=\"elite%20quest\"&gt;elite quest&lt;/a&gt; \"\"&lt;a href=\"The%20Astral%20Bloom\"&gt;The Astral Bloom&lt;/a&gt;\"\"."}
