{"id": "3189", "revid": "48095951", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3189", "title": "Might", "text": "Might is a &lt;a href=\"Paladin\"&gt;Paladin&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Skill\"&gt;Skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\n\"Caught up in the fervor of battle, the Paladin calls upon the power of righteousness and the strength of justice to add force to the attacks of his party. What would be glancing blows now strike their mark, and otherwise deflected strikes rend through armor to bite flesh.\"\nGeneral Information.\nMight is one of the first skills that the Paladin may learn. It increases weapon damage dealt by the Paladin and his allies around him at a certain range. It is useful in the very early stages of the game; however, it pales later in the game compared to &lt;a href=\"Concentration\"&gt;Concentration&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Fanaticism\"&gt;Fanaticism&lt;/a&gt; due to its inferior damage boost and lack of extra effects. Its advisable only to put a max of one or two points into it. &lt;a href=\"mercenaries\"&gt;mercenaries&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in Nightmare difficulty may have this skill naturally, giving other classes access to Might.\nThere is also an &lt;a href=\"item\"&gt;item&lt;/a&gt; that gives this Aura: the &lt;a href=\"runeword\"&gt;runeword&lt;/a&gt; ."}
{"id": "16209", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16209", "title": "Might (magic suffix)", "text": "Might is a &lt;a href=\"suffix\"&gt;suffix&lt;/a&gt; that can appear on &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;. It provides a small bonus to &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt can start spawning on items at &lt;a href=\"Item%20Level\"&gt;Item Level&lt;/a&gt; 10, but will not be able to spawn on all items until level 33.\nStats.\n\"Can appear on:\" &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic Items&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;\n\"Is available on:\" &lt;a href=\"Amulets\"&gt;Amulets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Belts\"&gt;Belts&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Circlets\"&gt;Circlets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Body%20Armor\"&gt;Body Armor&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rings\"&gt;Rings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gloves\"&gt;Gloves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Melee%20Weapons\"&gt;Melee Weapons&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shields\"&gt;Shields&lt;/a&gt;"}
