{"id": "31199", "revid": "5562046", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=31199", "title": "Missive to Maghda", "text": "Missive to Maghda is a two-part &lt;a href=\"Tomes\"&gt;tome&lt;/a&gt; found in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". \nPart 1 is found in the &lt;a href=\"Hidden%20Conclave\"&gt;Hidden Conclave&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Sandy%20Cellar\"&gt;Sandy Cellar&lt;/a&gt;, during the quests \"\"&lt;a href=\"Shadows%20in%20the%20Desert\"&gt;Shadows in the Desert&lt;/a&gt;\" or \"&lt;a href=\"City%20of%20Blood\"&gt;City of Blood&lt;/a&gt;\"\". The second part is found on a corpse in &lt;a href=\"Alcarnus\"&gt;Alcarnus&lt;/a&gt; during the latter quest.\nThey read as follows:\nPart 1\n\"&lt;a href=\"Maghda\"&gt;Maghda&lt;/a&gt;, this &lt;a href=\"The%20Nephalem\"&gt;\"hero\"&lt;/a&gt; means to attack you in Alcarnus. If I were you, I would set a trap at the &lt;a href=\"Khasim%20Outpost\"&gt;Khasim Outpost&lt;/a&gt;, but I am not you. For all I know, you wish to fail me again and force me to kill you. That would grieve me, though somehow...I think I could manage it. - &lt;a href=\"Belial\"&gt;Belial&lt;/a&gt;\"\nPart 2\n\"Maghda, such sad, sad tales have reached me of your truly abysmal failure to stop the enemy at the Khasim Outpost. But at least the enemy's &lt;a href=\"Leah\"&gt;spy&lt;/a&gt; has been found. Once we eliminate her and her allies, this obnoxious little &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary\"&gt;world&lt;/a&gt; will fall to me...and perhaps you, if you survive. - Belial\""}
