{"id": "47770", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=47770", "title": "Abandoned Journal", "text": "The Abandoned Journal is a &lt;a href=\"tome\"&gt;tome&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\". It is found in a in &lt;a href=\"Scosglen\"&gt;Scosglen&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt reads as follows:\n\"Do you hear it? The howling? The hideous howling? I no longer know whether that horrific sound is in the air or in my head. My mind will not be still since I've come to this place.\"\n\"So many have disappeared, taken down into the earth by...something...never to be seen again. Is that the fate awaiting me? I am drawn to it, and have no will to resist.\""}
