{"id": "19232", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19232", "title": "Affix", "text": "An affix refers to a modification to the basic form of an &lt;a href=\"item\"&gt;item&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"monster\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt;.\nItem attributes are usually determined by a base item plus the attributes of one or more affixes, each of which corresponds to descriptive word(s) in the names of &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic Items&lt;/a&gt;. Attributes of &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt; are also determined by affixes, but without the descriptors in the name.\n&lt;a href=\"Elite%20Monsters\"&gt;Elite Monsters&lt;/a&gt; usually have one or more abilities granted by standardized \"affixes\", in addition to the statistics and abilities of normal monsters of their type."}
