{"id": "48788", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=48788", "title": "Alexius", "text": "Alexius was one of the guards stationed at &lt;a href=\"Stormpoint%20Keep\"&gt;Stormpoint Keep&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231272\"&gt;time&lt;/a&gt; the &lt;a href=\"Stormpoint\"&gt;island&lt;/a&gt; was besieged by the &lt;a href=\"Cult%20of%20Terror\"&gt;Cult of Terror&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nAlexius was one of the survivors of the Cult of Terror's main attack on Stormpoint. Later, he was patrolling the keep's courtyard with his comrades &lt;a href=\"Broos\"&gt;Broos&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Crommlinc\"&gt;Crommlinc&lt;/a&gt; when they were attacked by Cultists. He was killed, along with Crommlinc in the attack, and their &lt;a href=\"corpse\"&gt;corpse&lt;/a&gt;s dragged away. Their bodies were added to a sculptor's pile, which bound their &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;s to the statue in torment. Broos, together with an &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt; was able to free them.\nIn-game.\nAlexius is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; seen in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". His ghost is featured in the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20Side%20Quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; \"&lt;a href=\"Bound%20to%20Death\"&gt;Bound to Death&lt;/a&gt;\"."}
