{"id": "44607", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=44607", "title": "Ammar", "text": " is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". He is featured in the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20Side%20Quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; \"&lt;a href=\"Mastery%20and%20Nothingness\"&gt;Mastery and Nothingness&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBiography.\nAmmar was sent by the &lt;a href=\"Patriarch\"&gt;Patriarch&lt;/a&gt;s to investigate the rot that had spread from the &lt;a href=\"Sanctified%20Earth%20Monastery\"&gt;Sanctified Earth Monastery&lt;/a&gt; to its surrounding areas at &lt;a href=\"Mount%20Zavain\"&gt;Mount Zavain&lt;/a&gt;. Upon reaching the monastery, he met a passing &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt; who he invited to help him investigate. \nIn the course of the investigation, he learnt that the taint belonged to a \"&lt;a href=\"Skarn\"&gt;God of Retribution&lt;/a&gt;\", and was introduced to the monastery by a monk named &lt;a href=\"Dravec\"&gt;Dravec&lt;/a&gt;. He also learnt that apart from the God of Retribution, the shadow of an &lt;a href=\"Ancient%20Nightmare\"&gt;ancient hatred&lt;/a&gt; also lurked around the monastery."}
