{"id": "40811", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=40811", "title": "Ancient Arena", "text": "The Ancient Arena is located on &lt;a href=\"Bilefen\"&gt;Bilefen&lt;/a&gt;.\nLore.\nIn ancient times, &lt;a href=\"nephalem\"&gt;nephalem&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"warrior\"&gt;warrior&lt;/a&gt;s tested themselves against each other in the arena. &lt;a href=\"Demon\"&gt;Demon&lt;/a&gt;ic energy caused these fallen warriors to rise.\nIn-game.\nThe Ancient Arena is a \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\" Bilefen zone. It is the zone's PvP arena.\nA chest spawns in the arena every three hours. Players are able to fight over it."}
{"id": "3218", "revid": "35609904", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3218", "title": "Ancient Armor", "text": "Ancient Armor is a piece of &lt;a href=\"Body%20Armor\"&gt;Body Armor&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". It is the most powerful form of armor in the game as far as defense goes in normal mode, though it pays for this with a high strength requirement. It is classified as medium armor."}
