{"id": "28429", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=28429", "title": "Ancient Guardian", "text": "Ancient Guardian, Horadric Mage Construct,\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Super%20Unique\"&gt;Super Unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sand%20Dweller\"&gt;Sand Dweller&lt;/a&gt; found in &lt;a href=\"Forgotten%20Ruins\"&gt;Forgotten Ruins&lt;/a&gt; in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nHe guards the head of &lt;a href=\"Zoltun%20Kulle\"&gt;Zoltun Kulle&lt;/a&gt;, spawning after it is taken. Killing him is optional, for nothing prevents the player from leaving once they have the head. Unlike other monsters, Ancient Guardian will not stop pursuing a fleeing player until they leave the dungeon.\nIn combat, it has Extra Health and Knockback affixes. He also moves a bit faster than normal Sand Dwellers."}
