{"id": "26276", "revid": "5562046", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26276", "title": "Ancient Pyre", "text": "Ancient Pyre is a location that may spawn in the &lt;a href=\"Southern%20Highlands\"&gt;Southern Highlands&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Act%20I%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act I&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". This is where the event &lt;a href=\"The%20Revenge%20of%20Gharbad\"&gt;The Revenge of Gharbad&lt;/a&gt; can be found.\nIt always spawns at the same location (to the north of the entrance, the eastern part of the map). If &lt;a href=\"Gharbad%20the%20Weak%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Gharbad&lt;/a&gt; is not there, &lt;a href=\"Chupa%20Khazra\"&gt;Chupa Khazra&lt;/a&gt; may spawn instead.\nThe pyre itself is a burial ground, with a single mummified &lt;a href=\"Khazra\"&gt;Khazra&lt;/a&gt; in the center."}
{"id": "26555", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26555", "title": "Ancient Ruins of Dholmour", "text": "Ancient Ruins of Dholmour is a small dungeon that can be found in &lt;a href=\"Battlefields%20of%20Eternity\"&gt;Battlefields of Eternity&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nThis dungeon houses a special encounter with the &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Monsters\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Barbed%20Lurker\"&gt;Barbed Lurker&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Mulliuqs%20the%20Horrid\"&gt;Mulliuqs the Horrid&lt;/a&gt;. He waits at the end of a three-part path infested by Scouring &lt;a href=\"Scouring%20Charger\"&gt;Chargers&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scouring%20Lobber\"&gt;Scouring Lobber&lt;/a&gt;s as well as &lt;a href=\"Winged%20Talus\"&gt;Winged Talus&lt;/a&gt;es. The heroes must reach him, then chase him back to the entrance in three phases as he retreats from their attack, spawning new swarms of enemies each time. A &lt;a href=\"Scavenging%20Tunneler\"&gt;Scavenging Tunneler&lt;/a&gt; may also reveal itself near the end of the fight."}
