{"id": "20611", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20611", "title": "Angel Hair Braid", "text": "Angel Hair Braid is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Belts\"&gt;belt&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;. It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 50 to drop.\nThe unique affix (added in 2.1) grants &lt;a href=\"Punish\"&gt;Punish&lt;/a&gt; all rune effects: the damage type is determined by the currently selected rune.\nIt has a guaranteed &lt;a href=\"indestructible\"&gt;indestructible&lt;/a&gt; property. It also one of the few items having more than six affixes."}
