{"id": "3398", "revid": "1687225", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3398", "title": "Angelic Raiment", "text": "Angelic Raiment is an &lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;item set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIt boasts a high-defense armor and useful jewelry for its level. It is one of the most powerful early-mid game sets that is made more accessible by its excellent partial set bonuses, with even many end-game builds benefiting from the massive increase to &lt;a href=\"Attack%20Rating\"&gt;Attack Rating&lt;/a&gt; that its rings provide with partial set bonuses. The full set is marred by its very weak weapon, however.\nSet.\n (3 items)"}
