{"id": "46288", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46288", "title": "Anica's Claim (Tome)", "text": "Anica's Claim is a &lt;a href=\"tome\"&gt;tome&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", found in the &lt;a href=\"Anica%27s%20Claim\"&gt;Anica's Claim&lt;/a&gt; . It can be found in the Tomb of the Frozen section.\nIt reads as follows:\n\"\"Mother &lt;a href=\"Anica\"&gt;Anica&lt;/a&gt; says the &lt;a href=\"Light\"&gt;Light&lt;/a&gt; delivered us to these mines. She says...she says we were sent here to do good work, to deliver good materials to the fine folk at &lt;a href=\"Kor%20Valar\"&gt;Kor Valar&lt;/a&gt;. She says it's part of &lt;a href=\"Inarius\"&gt;the Father's&lt;/a&gt; grand design.\"\"\n\"I'm faithful, truly I am. But to say this is the Father's work? Oh no, I hear strange noises. I catch whiffs of a foul odor. And the structures?\"\n\"We've found sharp wooden poles scattered throughout the tunnels. Obviously handmade, but not by us. Who made them? Hmm, why? And what is this place exactly?\""}
