{"id": "45594", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=45594", "title": "Another adventurer", "text": "Zatham is a mysterious &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt; that came to aid of &lt;a href=\"Stormpoint\"&gt;Stormpoint&lt;/a&gt; when it was invaded by the &lt;a href=\"Cult%20of%20Terror\"&gt;Cult of Terror&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nWhen the Cult of Terror was close to breaching the &lt;a href=\"Stormpoint%20Battlement\"&gt;Stormpoint Battlement&lt;/a&gt;, a stranger came to the defenders aid, killing half dozen cultists without breaking a sweat. After they let him in, he asked the &lt;a href=\"Commander%20Kenton\"&gt;commander&lt;/a&gt; for a way into the &lt;a href=\"Abandoned%20Prison\"&gt;Abandoned Prison&lt;/a&gt;. The commander refused, so Zatham began to plan a strategy to attack the cult and stop their advancement to the prison.\nLuckily, &lt;a href=\"the%20Shard-seeker\"&gt;another adventurer&lt;/a&gt; came to Stormpoint's rescue, also looking for a way into the prison. Grateful for the assistance, he told the Shard-seeker to stop the cultists from advancing through the sea while he would go after their aerial reinforcement. After that, he jumps through a portal to go after the &lt;a href=\"Howling%20Terror\"&gt;Howling Terror&lt;/a&gt; as it was flying by.\nZatham meets the Shard-seeker again in the Warden's office just after a &lt;a href=\"Deepstrider%20Behemoth\"&gt;sea behemoth&lt;/a&gt; captures a &lt;a href=\"Fern\"&gt;little girl&lt;/a&gt; in its rampage over it's &lt;a href=\"Woodruh\"&gt;master's&lt;/a&gt; death. They chase the monster back to &lt;a href=\"Deepstrider%20Lair\"&gt;its lair&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"Esmund\"&gt;girl's brother&lt;/a&gt; dives into the water to save her. Zatham tells the Shard-seeker to distract the beast while he would rescue the children. Unfortunately, the boy drowned before he could be saved.\nAfter rescuing them, thay were attacked by cultists; which was a distraction for &lt;a href=\"Akinees\"&gt;their leader&lt;/a&gt; to steal the &lt;a href=\"Worldstone\"&gt;Worldstone&lt;/a&gt; shard."}
